===Etymology===
Despite STEDT, probably not related to {{och-l|盈|to fill; full, surplus}}, in light of Baxter and Sagart's reconstruction of the Old Chinese pronunciation. Instead, note similarities to {{cog|tbq-lob-pro|*ʔoŋ¹|t=to win, complete}}, whence {{cog|my|အောင်|t=to be victorious}}.

